cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper deals with deep neural networks and their training for image classification tasks, which are typically covered in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of semi-supervised learning, which falls under the sub-category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques for filtering noisy labels, which is relevant to the sub-category of computation and language (cs.CL).
